        <name>COBS_DEFAULT_DELIMITER</name>
        <initializer>0x00</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Default COBS delimiter value. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The standard COBS delimiter is zero (0x00). This is the delimiter value used when COBS_FLAG_CUSTOM_DELIMITER is not specified. </para>
